    <item>
      <title>中国在刺激措施下发行欧元债券以测试市场情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-markets-euro-bond-in-test-of-sentiment-amid-stimulus-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，中国开始发行三年来首笔以欧元计价的债券，而全球投资者则密切关注着中国为重振放缓的经济而采取的一系列措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-markets-euro-bond-in-test-of-sentiment-amid-stimulus-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中国刺激计划乐观情绪推动，铁矿石价格回升至每吨 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/iron-ore-heads-back-toward-100-a-ton-on-china-stimulus-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测中国的大规模刺激计划将有助于提振需求，铁矿石价格连续第二天强劲上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/iron-ore-heads-back-toward-100-a-ton-on-china-stimulus-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行称中国可能加速货币宽松</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/china-may-accelerate-monetary-easing-standard-chartered-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行中国宏观战略主管刘贝琪讨论了中国为提振经济和陷入困境的房地产市场所做的努力，以及对金融市场的影响。中国人民银行行长潘功胜周二宣布下调存款准备金率、七天政策利率和现有抵押贷款利率。刘贝琪在“彭博：中国秀”上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/china-may-accelerate-monetary-easing-standard-chartered-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着股市飙升，中国国家队 ETF 的流入量增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-s-national-team-etfs-see-inflows-pick-up-as-stocks-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受主权基金青睐的中国交易所交易基金 (ETF) 周二资金流入增加，表明政府购买可能在 2020 年年中以来最大的境内股市上涨中发挥了作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-s-national-team-etfs-see-inflows-pick-up-as-stocks-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:58:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激政策持续乐观推动中国股市延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chinese-stocks-extend-gains-on-continued-stimulus-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者继续押注北京方面最新的刺激措施将有助于推动市场好转并提振中国低迷的经济，中国股市周三延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chinese-stocks-extend-gains-on-continued-stimulus-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出口商担忧导致泰铢升至 2022 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/baht-rises-to-strongest-since-march-2022-amid-exporters-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国刺激计划提振了全球风险资产，泰铢升至 30 个月来的最高水平，这给泰国央行带来了采取行动抑制泰铢升值的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/baht-rises-to-strongest-since-march-2022-amid-exporters-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:27:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据支持进一步降息，金价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-high-as-us-data-supports-deeper-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国数据疲软，进一步降息的可能性增强，黄金价格继上一交易日上涨逾 1% 后，再创历史新高。白银价格接近四个月来最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-high-as-us-data-supports-deeper-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币兑美元汇率自 2023 年 5 月以来首次突破 7</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/yuan-rallies-past-7-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者消化了一系列支持中国经济的措施，且美联储近期降息导致美元处于弱势，人民币兑美元汇率 16 个月来首次突破 7 大关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/yuan-rallies-past-7-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:09:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突和中国刺激计划成为焦点，油价持续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因交易商关注中东局势发展以及中国刺激措施对需求的影响，油价在创下一周多以来最大涨幅后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 23:36:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市、货币因对中国的乐观情绪而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国广泛刺激计划推动，亚洲股市连续第二天上涨，人民币也走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
